---
title: Turkey Ragù with Orzo and Cheesy Toasts
description: This orzo-centric meal packs on ragù flavour on a time-crunch! Savoury turkey, spinach and crushed tomatoes are the building blocks of a delicious sauce that gets paired with buttery orzo pasta. Can't forget the cheesy garlic bread, to scoop up every morsel!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragu-a-la-dinde-8e4f736b.jpg
